regex_utils contains: *RegexLetter* structure which holds the building blocks of *RegexWord* structure, getting a pointer to the sturcture and freeing.

reader_utils contains: *Reader* structure for some file if filename is not NULL, o.w stdin, the structue keeps count on the bytes and lines read, getting a pointer to the sturcture and freeing.

grep_flags contains: *GrepFlags* a structure which holds the inputs of the program, getting a pointer to the sturcture and freeing.
